# Aerospace News Scraper

This Python script scrapes the latest aerospace-related articles from two websites:
- [Simple Flying](https://simpleflying.com/)
- [SpaceNews](https://spacenews.com/)

It extracts headlines and links, combines them into a single dataset, and saves the results into a CSV file (`aerospace_news.csv`).

